subject: Appointment of a regional coordinator of the Employment Insurance Board of Appeal
precis: Appointment of Trisha Elie of Laval, Quebec, to be a regional coordinator of the Employment Insurance Board of Appeal, to hold office during pleasure on a full-time basis for a term of four years, effective January 12, 2026.
